Date: September 8, 1998  
Abstract: Alan E. Gelfand is a Professor in the Department of Statistics at the University of Connecti-cut, Storrs, CT 06269. Sujit K. Sahu is a Lecturer at the School of Mathematics, University of Wales, Cardiff, CF2 4YH, UK. The research of the first author was supported in part by NSF grant DMS 9301316 while the second author was supported in part by an EPSRC grant from UK. The authors thank Brad Carlin, Kate Cowles, Gareth Roberts and an anonymous referee for valuable comments. 
